## 13. Anti-scope (DO NOT do in this TZ)

- ❌ Do NOT migrate BEFORE TZ-103 merges (consumer code shares scope).
- ❌ Do NOT batch-migrate all 27 tables in one commit (overwhelming for reviewers).
- ❌ Do NOT remove hand-rolled patterns without booting the migration target first.
- ❌ Do NOT change `pi-table` / `pi-switch` etc. visual defaults (will cascade signal-loss across kit showcase).
- ❌ Do NOT introduce `pi-menu` / `pi-tabs` adoption in pages (kit-only).
- ❌ Do NOT migrate pages that have no clear Pi-* equivalent (e.g. products/product-detail.page.ts uses raw `<table>` inside `<app-pi-card>` slots; defer).
- ❌ Do NOT split this into TZ-104a/b/c/d (fits one TZ with three sub-tasks; per-sub-task atomic commits).
- ❌ Do NOT change `data-test` attribute names — propagation only, no rename.

